WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.503 --> 00:00:04.538
I'M FORREST MACNEIL,
AND AS ALWAYS,

00:00:04.571 --> 00:00:06.974
I WILL REVIEW ANY EXPERIENCE
YOU WANT ME TO,

00:00:07.007 --> 00:00:08.308
NO MATTER WHAT IT IS.

00:00:08.342 --> 00:00:09.776
- YOU READY, FORREST?
- YES, I AM.

00:00:09.810 --> 00:00:11.278
- OKAY.

00:00:11.311 --> 00:00:13.380
THIS COMES FROM NICK
IN SYOSSET, NEW YORK.

00:00:13.413 --> 00:00:14.648
- AHA.

00:00:14.681 --> 00:00:16.049
- HEY, FORREST.

00:00:16.083 --> 00:00:18.285
SO, ON THE BACK OF THIS BOX
OF PANCAKE MIX,

00:00:18.318 --> 00:00:20.721
THEY TELL YOU HOW TO MAKE
15 PANCAKES,

00:00:20.754 --> 00:00:23.290
BUT IT DOESN'T TELL YOU
HOW TO MAKE ANY FEWER THAN THAT.

00:00:23.323 --> 00:00:25.826
SO HERE'S THE THING--
I LIVE ALONE.

00:00:25.859 --> 00:00:28.829
DO THEY EXPECT ME
TO EAT 15 PANCAKES?

00:00:28.862 --> 00:00:32.633
WHAT'S IT LIKE
TO EAT 15 PANCAKES?

00:00:32.666 --> 00:00:34.701
- NO. REALLY?

00:00:34.735 --> 00:00:36.303
THAT'S THE, UH--

00:00:36.336 --> 00:00:38.005
THAT'S THE PROFOUND
LIFE EXPERIENCE

00:00:38.038 --> 00:00:39.973
HE WANTS TO KNOW ABOUT--
EATING 15 PANCAKES?

00:00:40.007 --> 00:00:42.209
- THAT'S HIS REQUEST, SO...

00:00:42.242 --> 00:00:45.145
- YES, THAT IS...
[clears throat]

00:00:45.179 --> 00:00:46.547
THE REQUEST
THAT HAS BEEN MADE.

00:00:46.580 --> 00:00:48.215
OKAY, NICK,

00:00:48.248 --> 00:00:50.050
I'M GOING TO COVER YOUR REQUEST
IN BUTTER AND SYRUP

00:00:50.083 --> 00:00:52.553
AND DIG IN TO TRY TO FIND
SOME IMPORTANT MEANING

00:00:52.586 --> 00:00:56.890
IN A GIANT, STEAMING PILE
OF FLAPJACKS.

00:00:56.924 --> 00:00:59.193
EATING 15 PANCAKES.

00:00:59.226 --> 00:01:01.528
- YUM.
- AHH.

00:01:01.562 --> 00:01:03.197
THOUGH THIS TASK
WAS CLEARLY MORE SUITED

00:01:03.230 --> 00:01:05.499
TO A FRATERNITY BROTHER
WHO HAD LOST A BET

00:01:05.532 --> 00:01:06.900
THAN TO A LIFE REVIEWER,

00:01:06.934 --> 00:01:09.069
I PREPARED MY STOMACH
AND MY NERVES

00:01:09.069 --> 00:01:12.539
FOR A VERY LARGE BREAKFAST.

00:01:12.573 --> 00:01:14.575
THE WORLD RECORD
FOR PANCAKES EATEN

00:01:14.608 --> 00:01:18.111
IN ONE SITTING
IS 73 PANCAKES.

00:01:18.145 --> 00:01:19.546
THAT IS HELD
BY A RUSSIAN MAN

00:01:19.580 --> 00:01:22.282
WHOSE LIFE MUST BE
AN UNENDURABLE HELLSCAPE

00:01:22.316 --> 00:01:24.418
OF EXCRUCIATING SADNESS.

00:01:24.451 --> 00:01:26.119
PERSONALLY, I DOUBT
I'VE EVER HAD

00:01:26.153 --> 00:01:27.855
MORE THAN TWO PANCAKES
IN A MONTH.

00:01:27.888 --> 00:01:30.757
- OKAY, FIVE TALL STACKS
OF PANCAKES.

00:01:30.791 --> 00:01:32.526
- YES.

00:01:32.559 --> 00:01:34.294
- THEY SAY BACK IN THE KITCHEN
IF YOU CAN FINISH IT ALL,

00:01:34.328 --> 00:01:35.863
WE'LL PUT YOUR PICTURE
UP ON THE WALL.

00:01:35.896 --> 00:01:39.233
- MM, NO, I DON'T THINK SO,
BUT THANK YOU.

00:01:39.266 --> 00:01:40.734
MAY I HAVE AN ENORMOUS AMOUNT
OF WATER, PLEASE?

00:01:40.767 --> 00:01:43.103
- YOU GOT IT.
- ALL RIGHT, GOOD.

00:01:43.136 --> 00:01:47.274
THIS CERTAINLY IS
AN UPSETTING NUMBER OF PANCAKES.

00:01:47.307 --> 00:01:48.709
HERE WE GO.

00:01:48.742 --> 00:01:51.712
[dramatic music]

00:01:51.745 --> 00:01:54.314
♪

00:01:54.348 --> 00:01:56.149
THEY'RE TASTY...

00:01:56.183 --> 00:01:57.985
FOR NOW.

00:01:58.018 --> 00:02:02.089
♪

00:02:02.122 --> 00:02:04.091
THREE PANCAKES IN,
AND I ALREADY FEEL

00:02:04.124 --> 00:02:07.294
THAT I HAVE
GREATLY OVERINDULGED.

00:02:07.327 --> 00:02:09.563
I AM FULL OF PANCAKES.

00:02:09.596 --> 00:02:12.232
ANY RATIONAL PERSON
FEELING THE WAY I DO NOW

00:02:12.266 --> 00:02:14.134
WOULD DEFINITELY STOP.

00:02:14.168 --> 00:02:16.170
[chuckles]

00:02:18.705 --> 00:02:26.079
♪

00:02:26.079 --> 00:02:29.449
THERE'S A VERY LOUD THRUMMING
IN MY EARS.

00:02:31.451 --> 00:02:34.154
THE BLOOD FEELS VERY SLOW.

00:02:35.622 --> 00:02:38.492
OH, GOD.

00:02:38.525 --> 00:02:42.262
I HAVE NOW EATEN
TEN PANCAKES,

00:02:42.296 --> 00:02:45.199
AND ON THE BRIGHT SIDE,
I CAN SEE THE LIGHT

00:02:45.232 --> 00:02:49.136
AT THE END OF THIS
DISGUSTING TUNNEL, BUT...

00:02:49.169 --> 00:02:52.206
IT HAS NOW BEEN 45 MINUTES

00:02:52.239 --> 00:02:53.473
SINCE I STARTED EATING,

00:02:53.507 --> 00:02:58.312
AND THE PANCAKES
ARE NO LONGER HOT.

00:02:58.345 --> 00:03:00.147
THESE AREN'T FOOD.

00:03:09.389 --> 00:03:12.459
- YOU'RE GONNA BE FINE, BABY.

00:03:12.492 --> 00:03:15.963
- WITH 1 1/2 PANCAKES TO GO,
I HAD HIT A WALL.

00:03:16.063 --> 00:03:18.465
MY PRODUCER, GRANT,
MADE THE UNPRECEDENTED MOVE

00:03:18.498 --> 00:03:20.367
OF STEPPING OUT
FROM BEHIND THE CAMERAS

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:23.337
TO PROVIDE MUCH-NEEDED
MORAL SUPPORT.

00:03:23.370 --> 00:03:26.406
- HEY, YOU KNOW YOU GOT
TO FINISH THESE PANCAKES, RIGHT?

00:03:26.440 --> 00:03:28.075
- YEAH.

00:03:40.854 --> 00:03:42.890
- YOU DO, MAN.
- MM.

00:03:42.923 --> 00:03:45.092
- THIS IS YOUR SHOW.
DON'T BAIL ON IT.

00:03:45.125 --> 00:03:46.493
- GO AWAY, PLEASE.

00:03:46.527 --> 00:03:48.095
- I'M JUST DOING
WHAT YOU TOLD ME TO DO.

00:03:48.095 --> 00:03:49.429
I'M NOT GOING TO LET YOU
BACK DOWN.

00:03:49.463 --> 00:03:51.331
REMEMBER?

00:03:51.365 --> 00:03:54.501
"EVEN IF I BEG TO STOP,
DON'T LET ME."

00:03:54.535 --> 00:03:55.736
THAT'S WHAT YOU SAID.

00:03:55.769 --> 00:03:58.739
- THIS ONE IS REALLY STUPID.

00:04:07.047 --> 00:04:08.782
- DO YOU REMEMBER
WHAT YOU TOLD ME

00:04:08.815 --> 00:04:10.551
ABOUT THE GUY
WHO SPENT ALL HIS TIME

00:04:10.584 --> 00:04:13.086
GROWING FUNGUS ON A STICK?

00:04:13.120 --> 00:04:15.522
AND EVERYBODY TOLD HIM
TO KNOCK IT OFF,

00:04:15.556 --> 00:04:16.924
AND HE WAS GONNA,

00:04:16.957 --> 00:04:18.592
UNTIL IT TURNED OUT
TO BE PENICILLIN.

00:04:18.625 --> 00:04:20.194
- MM-HMM.

00:04:20.227 --> 00:04:23.964
- THIS COULD BE
YOUR PENICILLIN, FORREST.

00:04:24.064 --> 00:04:27.067
- [sighs]

00:04:35.976 --> 00:04:38.946
[suspenseful music]

00:04:38.979 --> 00:04:46.987
♪

00:04:55.429 --> 00:04:56.830
[laughter,
cheers, and applause]

00:04:56.864 --> 00:04:59.333
- YOU DID IT.
YOU DID IT!

00:04:59.366 --> 00:05:02.903
[laughing]

00:05:02.936 --> 00:05:05.939
OKAY, I'LL TAKE THIS
WHEN YOU'RE READY.

00:05:11.044 --> 00:05:12.579
- AS I LEFT THE RESTAURANT,

00:05:12.613 --> 00:05:15.182
I SCANNED MY SOUL
FOR SOME GREATER WISDOM

00:05:15.215 --> 00:05:16.950
TO SHARE WITH HUMANITY.

00:05:17.050 --> 00:05:19.219
[heaving]

00:05:24.224 --> 00:05:25.959
[spits]
UGH.

00:05:26.059 --> 00:05:28.629
[groaning softly]

00:05:35.235 --> 00:05:36.503
YEAH, THERE'S NOT REALLY

00:05:36.537 --> 00:05:38.172
A WHOLE LOT MORE
TO SAY ABOUT THAT.

00:05:38.205 --> 00:05:39.873
IT WAS EXTREMELY UNPLEASANT
AND SHOULD BE AVOIDED

00:05:39.907 --> 00:05:41.341
AT ALL COSTS.

00:05:41.375 --> 00:05:44.378
EATING 15 PANCAKES--
HALF A STAR.

